n  - Updated all contract examples and tests to use the new versions\r\n\r\n  ### Tooling Improvements\r\n  - **Added version bump automation script** (`scripts/version-bump.sh`)\r\n    - Auto-detects which modules need version bumps based on git changes\r\n    - Generates changelog from git commits\r\n    - Supports dry-run mode for preview\r\n    - Handles all dependency formats including TOML sections with `=` prefix\r\n\r\n  - **Added dependency checker script** (`scripts/check-dependencies.sh`)\r\n    - Scans all Cargo.toml files for outdated dependencies\r\n    - Auto-detects current versions from source files\r\n    - Supports automatic fixing with `--fix` flag\r\n    - Provides detailed reports on version mismatches\r\n\r\n  - **Added build automation scripts**\r\n    - `scripts/meta-build-wasm.sh`: Builds all WASM contracts\r\n    - `scripts/meta-update-all.sh`: Updates all contract metadata\r\n\r\n  ### Bug Fixes\r\n  - Fixed typos across the codebase and added typo checker workflow\r\n  - Fixed CHANGELOG ordering\r\n  - Fixed version-bump script to handle files without trailing newlines\r\n  - Fixed dependency version extraction for `=` prefixed versions\r\n\r\n  ## Testing\r\n  - All tests pass\r\n  - Version bump script tested on various contract examples\r\n  - Dependency checker validated across entire repository\r\n\r\n  ## Breaking Changes\r\n  None - This is a compatible version update.\r\n\r\n  ## Checklist\r\n  - [x] All dependencies updated to new versions\r\n  - [x] Tests passing\r\n  - [x] CHANGELOG updated\r\n  - [x] Version history updated in `framework/meta/src/version_history.rs`\r\n  - [x] Scripts tested and documented", "created_at": "2025-06-11T21:05:07Z", "updated_at": "2025-06-11T21:30:55Z", "closed_at": "2025-06-11T21:30:55Z", "merged_at": "2025-06-11T21:30:55Z", "merge_commit_sha": "a0128b2148f7b44212c63543e2fc75ccb0c68a8b", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone